    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >      你将摇身一变成为一名初出茅庐的经营者，负责街区的经营，在这里，你需要不断的开设各类店铺，来逐步发展的你的街区，同时还要兼容店铺内的经营，各色各样的店铺等你来运作，下一个街区是属于你的！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏特点：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211780/extras/79826ecd96e673710c53a411e1f37654.avif?t=1728891235\" width=600 height=128 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们有各种不同类型的饮食店铺，包括汉堡、咖啡、甜甜圈等，还有海量的特色主题提供你升级选择！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >           <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211780/extras/cc1d1e29495d7a33d43e28685ecd5ecd.poster.avif?t=1728891235\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211780/extras/cc1d1e29495d7a33d43e28685ecd5ecd.webm?t=1728891235\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211780/extras/cc1d1e29495d7a33d43e28685ecd5ecd.mp4?t=1728891235\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211780/extras/09f8ee57131b979e44e066c839621b65.avif?t=1728891235\" width=600 height=128 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过扭蛋机进行合成玩法，可以获得更多的餐品，每个店铺都有20种特色餐品提供选择，收集更多的餐品会获得更高的利润！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >            <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211780/extras/fa668d25b482fdfdade6855fc28f4efe.poster.avif?t=1728891235\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211780/extras/fa668d25b482fdfdade6855fc28f4efe.webm?t=1728891235\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211780/extras/fa668d25b482fdfdade6855fc28f4efe.mp4?t=1728891235\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211780/extras/b247d34f0d90bff7a89106e86d917789.avif?t=1728891235\" width=600 height=128 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >招募店长是你店铺开设的必要首先，通过升级餐品来不断培养店长，随着店长的等级提升，你将获得更多的店铺特权！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >           <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211780/extras/d850b7d9a53064ea5682a6e9c418f912.poster.avif?t=1728891235\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211780/extras/d850b7d9a53064ea5682a6e9c418f912.webm?t=1728891235\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211780/extras/d850b7d9a53064ea5682a6e9c418f912.mp4?t=1728891235\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211780/extras/39818d20258b8d8defd788190205f302.avif?t=1728891235\" width=600 height=128 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏内我们还加入了丰富的小游戏，如连连看，水果接力等，为玩家提供更多的乐趣！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >           <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211780/extras/a5be7792cda5d2232bb4f4f700ba167e.poster.avif?t=1728891235\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211780/extras/a5be7792cda5d2232bb4f4f700ba167e.webm?t=1728891235\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211780/extras/a5be7792cda5d2232bb4f4f700ba167e.mp4?t=1728891235\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只要你用心经营，街区生意肯定会津津日上，成为最佳经营者是你最终的目标!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-赶紧加入Idle Animal Plaza吧！来体验不一样的经营趣味，不在乏味！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-还有更多特色店铺和新的街区即将到来！</p>",
